<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
    <head>
        <meta charset="UTF-8">
        <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
        <title>Consumer - Getting Started</title>
        <link href="css/theme.css" rel="stylesheet" type="text/css">
        <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.4.0/css/all.min.css">
        <link rel="stylesheet" href="assets/css/global.css">
        <link rel="stylesheet" href="assets/css/consumer_getting_started.css">
        <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@400;500;600;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
        <style>
            /* Basic reset for preview consistency */
            body { margin: 0; padding: 0; font-family: sans-serif; background: #ffffff; }

            /* Premium Modern Header Styles */
            .modern-header {
                font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
                position: fixed;
                top: 0; left: 0; right: 0;
                height: 64px;
                background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.85);
                backdrop-filter: saturate(180%) blur(20px);
                -webkit-backdrop-filter: saturate(180%) blur(20px);
                border-bottom: 1px solid #e2e8f0;
                z-index: 300;
                display: flex;
                align-items: center;
                transition: all 0.3s ease;
            }
            .modern-header-inner {
                width: 100%;
                max-width: 1440px; /* Next.js Doc Container */
                margin: 0 auto;
                display: flex;
                align-items: center;
                height: 100%;
            }
            .modern-header-logo-plate {
                display: flex;
                align-items: center;
                padding-left: 32px; /* Standard container padding */
                width: 280px; /* Sidebar width match */
                min-width: 280px;
                height: 100%;
                box-sizing: border-box;
            }
            .modern-logo {
                display: flex;
                align-items: center;
                gap: 10px;
                cursor: pointer;
                text-decoration: none;
            }
            .modern-logo img {
                height: 28px;
                width: auto;
                border-radius: 6px;
                border: 1px solid rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.06);
            }
            .modern-logo span {
                font-size: 1.1rem;
                font-weight: 700;
                color: #0f172a;
                letter-spacing: -0.04em;
            }
            .modern-header-content {
                display: flex;
                align-items: center;
                justify-content: space-between;
                flex: 1;
                padding: 0 40px;
                height: 100%;
            }
            .modern-nav {
                display: flex;
                align-items: center;
                gap: 32px;
                height: 100%;
            }
            .modern-nav a {
                font-size: 0.875rem;
                font-weight: 500;
                color: #64748b; /* Lighter color for non-active */
                cursor: pointer;
                text-decoration: none;
                transition: color 0.2s ease;
                position: relative;
                padding: 0;
                display: flex;
                align-items: center;
                height: 100%;
            }
            .modern-nav a:hover {
                color: #0f172a;
            }
            .modern-nav a.active {
                color: #0f172a;
                font-weight: 600;
            }
            .modern-nav a.active::after {
                content: '';
                position: absolute;
                bottom: -1px;
                left: 0;
                right: 0;
                height: 2px;
                background-color: #0f172a;
                border-radius: 2px 2px 0 0;
                z-index: 2;
            }
            .modern-header-actions {
                display: flex;
                align-items: center;
                gap: 16px;
            }
            .modern-search-btn {
                display: flex;
                align-items: center;
                justify-content: space-between;
                width: 240px;
                padding: 6px 12px;
                background-color: #f1f5f9;
                border: 1px solid transparent;
                border-radius: 8px;
                font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
                font-size: 0.875rem;
                color: #64748b;
                cursor: pointer;
                transition: all 0.2s ease;
                outline: none;
            }
            .modern-search-btn:hover {
                background-color: #fff;
                border-color: #cbd5e1;
                color: #334155;
            }
            .modern-search-btn .search-content {
                display: flex;
                align-items: center;
                gap: 8px;
            }
            .modern-search-btn .search-icon {
                color: #94a3b8;
                font-size: 0.85rem;
            }
            .modern-search-shortcuts {
                display: flex;
                align-items: center;
                gap: 4px;
            }
            .modern-search-shortcuts kbd {
                font-family: ui-monospace, SFMono-Regular, Consolas, monospace;
                font-size: 0.7rem;
                font-weight: 500;
                padding: 2px 6px;
                background-color: #fff;
                border: 1px solid #e2e8f0;
                border-radius: 4px;
                color: #64748b;
            }
            .modern-cta-btn {
                padding: 8px 16px;
                background: #3b82f6 !important;
                color: #ffffff;
                border: 1px solid #3b82f6 !important;
                border-radius: 8px;
                font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
                font-size: 0.875rem;
                font-weight: 500;
                cursor: pointer;
                transition: all 0.2s ease;
            }
            .modern-cta-btn:hover {
                background: #1e293b;
            }

            /* Modern Layout Overrides - Containerized */
            .consumer-getting-started {
                max-width: 1440px !important;
                width: 100% !important;
                margin: 0 auto !important;
                padding-top: 64px !important;
                display: flex !important;
                background: #ffffff;
            }
            .cgs-sidebar {
                box-sizing: border-box !important;
                width: 280px !important;
                min-width: 280px !important;
                background: #ffffff !important; /* Minimal white */
                border-right: 1px solid #e2e8f0 !important;

                padding-left: 32px !important;
                padding-right: 24px !important;
                padding-top: 40px !important;
                position: sticky !important;
                top: 64px !important;
                height: calc(100vh - 64px) !important;
                overflow-y: auto !important;
            }

            .cgs-sidebar-header {
                padding: 0 !important;
                border-bottom: none !important;
                margin-bottom: 24px !important;
            }
            .cgs-sidebar-header h3 {
                color: #0f172a !important;
                font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif !important;
                font-size: 0.9375rem !important;
                font-weight: 600 !important;
                letter-spacing: -0.01em !important;
                text-transform: none !important;
                display: flex !important;
                align-items: center !important;
                cursor: pointer;
                gap: 8px !important;
                margin: 0 !important;
            }
            .cgs-sidebar-header h3 i {
                color: #0f172a !important;
                font-size: 1.1rem !important;
            }
            .cgs-nav-section {
                margin-bottom: 32px !important;
                padding: 0 !important;
            }
            .cgs-nav-section-label {
                font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif !important;
                font-size: 0.8125rem !important;
                font-weight: 500 !important;
                color: #0f172a !important; /* Darker heading for sections */
                text-transform: none !important; /* Minimalist capitalisation */
                letter-spacing: normal !important;
                padding: 0 0 12px 0 !important;
                display: block !important;
                margin: 0 !important;
                margin-top: 8px !important;
            }
            .cgs-nav-list {
                list-style: none;
                padding: 0;
                margin: 0 0 0 4px !important; /* Slight inset */
                border-left: 1px solid #e2e8f0 !important; /* The vertical line */
            }
            .cgs-nav-list li {
                padding: 0 !important;
                margin: 0 !important;
            }
            .cgs-nav-list li a {
                padding: 6px 16px !important;
                font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif !important;
                font-size: 0.875rem !important;
                color: #64748b !important; /* Light slate text */
                border-radius: 0 !important; /* NO RADIUS */
                background: transparent !important;
                transition: all 0.2s ease !important;
                font-weight: 400 !important; /* Thin natural font weight */
                display: flex !important;
                align-items: center !important; /* Icon center align! */
                line-height: 1.5 !important;
                gap: 12px !important;
                text-decoration: none !important;
                border-left: 1px solid transparent !important; /* Invisible active border anchor */
                margin-left: -1px !important; /* Overlap parent ul border */
            }
            .cgs-nav-list li a i {
                font-size: 0.875rem !important;
                color: #94a3b8 !important; /* Light gray icons */
                transition: color 0.2s ease !important;
                margin: 0 !important; /* Centered with flex */
            }
            .cgs-nav-list li a:hover {
                color: #0f172a !important;
                border-left-color: #94a3b8 !important; /* Subtle hover border line */
            }
            .cgs-nav-list li a:hover i {
                color: #64748b !important;
            }
            .cgs-nav-list li a.active {
                color: #3b82f6 !important; /* Blue text */
                font-weight: 500 !important; /* Semi-bold for active */
                border-left-color: #3b82f6 !important; /* SOLID thin blue active border line! */
                background: transparent !important; /* Minimal: no bg highlight */
            }
            .cgs-nav-list li a.active i {
                color: #3b82f6 !important;
            }

            .cgs-main {
                flex: 1;
                display: flex;
                min-width: 0 !important; /* Fix flex overflow */
                background: #ffffff !important;
            }
            .cgs-content-area {
                flex: 1;
                max-width: 860px !important;
                margin: 0;
                padding: 40px 64px !important;
                min-width: 0 !important;
            }

            /* Minimal TOC Override */
            .cgs-toc {
                width: 260px !important;
                min-width: 260px !important;
                padding: 40px 32px 32px 0 !important;
                position: sticky !important;
                top: 64px !important;
                align-self: flex-start !important;
                max-height: calc(100vh - 64px) !important;
                overflow-y: auto !important;
                border-left: none !important; /* Clean without arbitrary borders */
            }
            .cgs-toc-title {
                font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif !important;
                font-size: 0.875rem !important;
                color: #0f172a !important;
                margin: 0 0 16px 0 !important;
                text-transform: none !important; /* Clean mixed case */
                letter-spacing: normal !important;
                padding: 0 !important;
            }
            .cgs-toc-list {
                border-left: 1px solid #e2e8f0 !important;
                padding: 0 !important;
                margin: 0 !important;
            }
            .cgs-toc-link {
                font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif !important;
                font-size: 0.8125rem !important;
                color: #64748b !important;
                padding: 6px 0 6px 16px !important;
                border-left: 1px solid transparent !important;
                margin-left: -1px !important;
                font-weight: 400 !important;
                transition: all 0.15s ease !important;
            }
            .cgs-toc-link:hover {
                color: #0f172a !important;
                border-left-color: #94a3b8 !important;
            }
            .cgs-toc-link.active {
                color: #3b82f6 !important;
                border-left-color: #3b82f6 !important;
                font-weight: 500 !important;
            }

            /* Responsive YouTube iframe Wrapper */
            .video-wrapper {
                position: relative;
                padding-bottom: 56.25%; /* 16:9 Aspect Ratio */
                height: 0;
                overflow: hidden;
                border-radius: 12px;
                box-shadow: 0 4px 20px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.08); /* Premium shadow */
                margin: 32px 0;
                background: #0f172a;
            }
            .video-wrapper iframe {
                position: absolute;
                top: 0;
                left: 0;
                width: 100%;
                height: 100%;
                border: 0;
            }

            /* --- Comprehensive Mobile Responsiveness --- */
            @media (max-width: 1200px) {
                .cgs-toc { display: none !important; }
                .cgs-content-area { max-width: 100% !important; }
            }

            @media (max-width: 1024px) {
                /* Header shrinks */
                .modern-header-logo-plate { width: auto !important; min-width: 0 !important; padding-left: 24px !important; border-right: none !important; }
                .modern-nav { display: none !important; }
                .modern-search-btn { width: 180px !important; }

                /* Layout reflows */
                .cgs-sidebar { width: 240px !important; min-width: 240px !important; padding-left: 24px !important; border-right: 1px solid #e2e8f0 !important; }
                .cgs-content-area { padding: 40px 32px !important; }
            }

            @media (max-width: 768px) {
                /* Header: hide extra actions for space */
                .modern-header-logo-plate { padding-left: 16px !important; }
                .modern-header-content { padding: 0 16px !important; justify-content: flex-end !important; gap: 8px !important; }
                .modern-search-btn { display: none !important; } /* Hidden entirely */
                .modern-cta-btn { padding: 6px 12px !important; font-size: 0.8rem !important; }

                /* Sidebar: become a floating side-sheet */
                .cgs-sidebar {
                    position: fixed !important;
                    top: 64px !important;
                    left: 0 !important;
                    height: calc(100vh - 64px) !important;
                    transform: translateX(-100%) !important;
                    transition: transform 0.3s cubic-bezier(0.4, 0, 0.2, 1) !important;
                    z-index: 250 !important;
                    box-shadow: 4px 0 24px rgba(0,0,0,0.15) !important;
                    width: 280px !important;
                    padding-left: 24px !important;
                }
                .cgs-sidebar.open {
                    transform: translateX(0) !important;
                }
                .cgs-sidebar-overlay.show {
                    z-index: 240 !important; /* Ensure overlay naturally rests right beneath side-sheet */
                }

                /* Main Content breaks full width */
                .cgs-main { min-width: 100vw !important; max-width: 100vw !important; margin: 0 !important; display: block !important; }
                .cgs-content-area { padding: 24px 16px 80px !important; }
                .cgs-section-title { font-size: 1.5rem !important; }
                .cgs-page-title { font-size: 1.75rem !important; }
            }

            @media (max-width: 480px) {
                /* .modern-logo span { display: none !important; } Only show Logo Icon on tiny phones */
                .modern-cta-btn { font-size: 0.75rem !important; padding: 6px 10px !important; }
            }
        </style>
    </head>
    <body>
            <!-- Site Header -->
            <header class="modern-header">
                <div class="modern-header-inner">
                    <!-- Logo matching sidebar -->
                    <div class="modern-header-logo-plate">
                        <div class="modern-logo" onclick="load_page('index')">
                            <img src="https://dev.think4ever.com/uifiles/20260311/ed3d2c21991e3bef5e069713af9fa6ca/only_m_with_white_bg_logo.png" alt="MPay Network Logo">
                            <span>MPay Network</span>
                        </div>
                    </div>

                    <!-- Right header content -->
                    <div class="modern-header-content">
                        <nav class="modern-nav" aria-label="Main navigation">
                            <a onclick="load_page('index')">Overview</a>
                            <a onclick="load_page('merchant_docs_home')">Merchant</a>
                            <a onclick="load_page('consumer_docs_home')" class="active">Consumer</a>
                            <a onclick="load_page('blog_listing')">Blog</a>
                            <a onclick="load_page('changelog_page')">Changelog</a>
                        </nav>

                        <div class="modern-header-actions">
                            <button class="modern-search-btn" onclick="load_page('search_results')" aria-label="Search documentation">
                                <div class="search-content">
                                    <i class="fa fa-search search-icon" aria-hidden="true"></i>
                                    <span>Search docs...</span>
                                </div>
                                <div class="modern-search-shortcuts">
                                    <kbd>Ctrl</kbd>
                                    <kbd>K</kbd>
                                </div>
                            </button>
                            <button class="modern-cta-btn">
                                Dashboard
                            </button>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </header>
        <div class="consumer-getting-started">
            <!-- Skip to content -->
            <a href="#cgs-main-content" class="sr-only" style="position:absolute;left:-9999px;top:0;z-index:999;background:#fff;padding:8px 16px;">Skip to main content</a>
            <!-- Mobile sidebar toggle -->
            <button class="cgs-sidebar-toggle" id="cgsSidebarToggle" aria-label="Toggle navigation menu" aria-expanded="false">
                <i class="fa fa-bars"></i>
            </button>
            <!-- Sidebar overlay -->
            <div class="cgs-sidebar-overlay" id="cgsSidebarOverlay"></div>
            <!-- Sidebar -->
            <aside class="cgs-sidebar" id="cgsSidebar" role="navigation" aria-label="Consumer documentation navigation">
                <div class="cgs-sidebar-header">
                    <h3 onclick="load_page('consumer_docs_home')"> <i class="fa fa-book"></i>
        Consumer Wallet Docs </h3>
                </div>
                <nav class="cgs-nav-section">
                    <p class="cgs-nav-section-label">Getting Started</p>
                    <ul class="cgs-nav-list">
                        <li>
                            <a class="cgs-nav-link" onclick="load_page('consumer_docs_home')"><i class="fa fa-home"></i> Overview</a>
                        </li>
                        <li>
                            <a class="cgs-nav-link active" onclick="load_page('consumer_getting_started')"><i class="fa fa-rocket"></i> Getting Started</a>
                        </li>
                        <li>
                            <a class="cgs-nav-link" onclick="load_page('consumer_account_setup')"><i class="fa fa-user-plus"></i> Account Setup</a>
                        </li>
                    </ul>
                </nav>
                <nav class="cgs-nav-section">
                    <p class="cgs-nav-section-label">Using Your Wallet</p>
                    <ul class="cgs-nav-list">
                        <li>
                            <a class="cgs-nav-link" onclick="load_page('consumer_making_payments')"><i class="fa fa-credit-card"></i> Making Payments</a>
                        </li>
                        <li>
                            <a class="cgs-nav-link" onclick="load_page('consumer_wallet_management')"><i class="fa fa-wallet"></i> Wallet Management</a>
                        </li>
                        <li>
                            <a class="cgs-nav-link" onclick="load_page('consumer_p2p_transfers')"><i class="fa fa-exchange-alt"></i> P2P Transfers</a>
                        </li>
                    </ul>
                </nav>
                <nav class="cgs-nav-section">
                    <p class="cgs-nav-section-label">Settings & Support</p>
                    <ul class="cgs-nav-list">
                        <li>
                            <a class="cgs-nav-link" onclick="load_page('consumer_settings')"><i class="fa fa-cog"></i> Settings & Security</a>
                        </li>
                        <li>
                            <a class="cgs-nav-link" onclick="load_page('consumer_troubleshooting')"><i class="fa fa-life-ring"></i> Troubleshooting</a>
                        </li>
                    </ul>
                </nav>
                <nav class="cgs-nav-section" style="margin-top: 16px; padding-top: 16px; border-top: 1px solid var(--color-border, #bfdbfe);">
                    <p class="cgs-nav-section-label">Other Docs</p>
                    <ul class="cgs-nav-list">
                        <li>
                            <a class="cgs-nav-link" onclick="load_page('merchant_docs_home')"><i class="fa fa-store"></i> Merchant Wallet Docs</a>
                        </li>
                        <li>
                            <a class="cgs-nav-link" onclick="load_page('changelog_page')"><i class="fa fa-history"></i> Changelog</a>
                        </li>
                    </ul>
                </nav>
            </aside>
            <!-- Main content -->
            <div class="cgs-main">
                <main class="cgs-content-area" id="cgs-main-content">
                    <!-- Breadcrumb -->
                    <nav class="cgs-breadcrumb" aria-label="Breadcrumb">
                        <a onclick="load_page('index')">Docs</a>
                        <span class="separator"><i class="fa fa-chevron-right"></i></span>
                        <a onclick="load_page('consumer_docs_home')">Consumer Wallet</a>
                        <span class="separator"><i class="fa fa-chevron-right"></i></span>
                        <span class="current">Getting Started</span>
                    </nav>
                    <!-- Page title -->
                    <h1 class="cgs-page-title">Getting Started with Consumer Wallet</h1>
                    <p class="cgs-page-subtitle">Everything you need to download, install, and set up your mPay Consumer Wallet. Follow this step-by-step guide to start making fast, secure payments in minutes.</p>
                    <span class="cgs-time-badge"> <i class="fa fa-clock"></i>
        Estimated setup time: 5 minutes </span>
                        <div class="video-wrapper">
                            <!-- <video
                                controls
                                width="640"
                                height="360"
                                preload="metadata"
                                poster="https://via.placeholder.com/640x360?text=Loading+Video"
                                >
                                <source
                                    src="https://core1.moadbusglobal.com/walletconsolemc/mpay-docs/videos/mPay_Getting_Started_Female.mp4"
                                    type="video/mp4"
                                >
                                Your browser does not support the video tag.
                            </video> -->

                            <iframe width="560" height="315" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/Sklc_fQBmcs?si=jDeITHMlg_vvfPbs" title="YouTube video player" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin" allowfullscreen></iframe>
                        </div>
                    <!-- System Requirements -->
                    <section class="cgs-section" id="sec-requirements">
                        <h2 class="cgs-section-title">System Requirements</h2>
                        <p>Before downloading, make sure your device meets the minimum requirements:</p>
                        <div class="cgs-requirements">
                            <div class="cgs-requirement-card">
                                <div class="req-icon">
                                    <i class="fa fa-apple-alt"></i>
                                </div>
                                <div class="req-info">
                                    <h4>iOS</h4>
                                    <p>iOS 15.0 or later. Compatible with iPhone 8 and newer. Approximately 85 MB of storage required.</p>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                            <div class="cgs-requirement-card">
                                <div class="req-icon">
                                    <i class="fab fa-android"></i>
                                </div>
                                <div class="req-info">
                                    <h4>Android</h4>
                                    <p>Android 10.0 (API level 29) or later. Approximately 60 MB of storage required.</p>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="cgs-callout info">
                            <div class="cgs-callout-icon">
                                <i class="fa fa-info-circle"></i>
                            </div>
                            <div class="cgs-callout-content">
                                <strong>NFC Requirement</strong>
                                <p>For tap-to-pay functionality, your device must have NFC hardware. Most modern smartphones (iPhone 7+ and Android with NFC) support this feature.</p>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </section>
                    <!-- Download & Install -->
                    <section class="cgs-section" id="sec-download">
                        <h2 class="cgs-section-title">Download & Install</h2>
                        <p>mPay Consumer Wallet is available for free on both major app stores. Choose your platform below:</p>
                        <div class="cgs-download-buttons">
                            <a class="cgs-download-btn ios" href="#" aria-label="Download on the App Store"> <i class="fab fa-apple"></i> <div class="btn-text">
                                    <small>Download on the</small>
                                    <span>App Store</span>
                                </div> </a>
                            <a class="cgs-download-btn android" href="#" aria-label="Get it on Google Play"> <i class="fab fa-google-play"></i> <div class="btn-text">
                                    <small>Get it on</small>
                                    <span>Google Play</span>
                                </div> </a>
                        </div>
                        <h3 class="cgs-section-subtitle" id="sec-install-steps">Installation Steps</h3>
                        <div class="cgs-steps">
                            <div class="cgs-step" data-step="1">
                                <h4 class="cgs-step-title">Open your app store</h4>
                                <div class="cgs-step-content">
                                    Open the <strong>App Store</strong> (iOS) or <strong>Google Play Store</strong> (Android) on your device.
                                </div>
                            </div>
                            <div class="cgs-step" data-step="2">
                                <h4 class="cgs-step-title">Search for mPay Wallet</h4>
                                <div class="cgs-step-content">
                                    Type <code>mPay Consumer Wallet</code> in the search bar. Look for the official app with the mPay logo and "mPay Network" as the developer.
                                </div>
                            </div>
                            <div class="cgs-step" data-step="3">
                                <h4 class="cgs-step-title">Download and install</h4>
                                <div class="cgs-step-content">
                                    Tap <strong>Get</strong> (iOS) or <strong>Install</strong> (Android). The app will download and install automatically. You may be asked to authenticate with your device password, Face ID, or fingerprint.
                                </div>
                            </div>
                            <div class="cgs-step" data-step="4">
                                <h4 class="cgs-step-title">Open the app</h4>
                                <div class="cgs-step-content">
                                    Once installed, tap <strong>Open</strong> or find the mPay icon on your home screen. The app will launch with the welcome screen.
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="cgs-callout warning">
                            <div class="cgs-callout-icon">
                                <i class="fa fa-exclamation-triangle"></i>
                            </div>
                            <div class="cgs-callout-content">
                                <strong>Verify the Developer</strong>
                                <p>Always verify that the developer is listed as "mPay Network" before downloading. Do not install apps from unofficial sources.</p>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </section>
                    <!-- Sign Up -->
                    <section class="cgs-section" id="sec-signup">
                        <h2 class="cgs-section-title">Sign Up</h2>
                        <p>Creating your mPay account is quick and straightforward. You'll need a valid phone number and email address.</p>
                        <div class="cgs-steps">
                            <div class="cgs-step" data-step="1">
                                <h4 class="cgs-step-title">Are you an existing mPay Customer?</h4>
                                <div class="cgs-step-content">
                                    <p class="cgs-step-text">On the welcome screen, you will be prompted to select whether you <strong>"Are an existing customer?"</strong>. For new customers, tap the <strong>NO</strong> button. If you already have an account, select <strong>YES</strong> button instead.</p>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                            <div class="cgs-step" data-step="2">
                                <h4 class="cgs-step-title">Enroll New Consumer Form</h4>
                                <div class="cgs-step-content">
                                    <p class="cgs-step-text">User is taken to <strong> Enroll New Consumer </strong> form. </p>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                            <div class="cgs-step" data-step="3">
                                <h4 class="cgs-step-title">Required Customer Information</h4>
                                <p class="cgs-step-text">The <strong> User ID </strong>, <strong> E-mail Address </strong>, and <strong>Mobile Number</strong> should be unique for each customers.  <div class="cgs-callout cgs-callout-info">
                                        <div class="cgs-callout-icon">
                                            <i class="fa fa-info-circle"></i>
                                        </div>
                                        <div class="cgs-callout-text">During enrollment submission, the system verifies whether the <strong>User ID</strong>, <strong>E-mail Address</strong> and <strong>Mobile Number</strong> is already in use by existing mPay customers.
                                        </div>
                                    </div>
                            </div>
                            <div class="cgs-step" data-step="4">
                                <h4 class="cgs-step-title">Fill in all required fields</h4>
                                <div class="cgs-step-content">
                                    Enter your basic information:
                                    <ul>
                                        <li>
                                            <strong>First and Last Name</strong> — As it appears on your ID
                                        </li>
                                        <li>
                                            <strong>Email Address</strong> — A valid email for notifications and recovery
                                        </li>
                                        <li>
                                            <strong>Mobiler Number</strong> — Should be a valid mobile number that will receive SMS for verification
                                        </li>
                                        <li>
                                            <strong>Referral Code</strong> — Optional field for the referral code of the referring mPay customer.
                                        </li>
                                    </ul>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                            <div class="cgs-step" data-step="5">
                                <h4 class="cgs-step-title">Agree to terms</h4>
                                <div class="cgs-step-content">
                                    <p class="cgs-step-text">There are two required checkboxes to accept prior proceeding with enrollment:</p>
                                    <ul style="margin: 8px 0 0 20px; list-style: disc; line-height: 1.8; color: #1e3a8a; font-size: 0.9375rem;">
                                        <li>Accept <strong>Terms and Conditions</strong>
                                        </li>
                                        <li>Security Policy that  only one user is allowed per device which states "<i>I agree that enrolling a new customer will remove the existing account linked on this device.</i>"
                                        </li>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                            <div class="cgs-step" data-step="6">
                                <h4 class="cgs-step-title">Option to Use Email and Mobile in Merchant App</h4>
                                <div class="cgs-step-content">
</div>
                                <p class="cgs-step-text">There are two required checkboxes to accept prior proceeding with enrollment:</p>
                                <ul style="margin: 8px 0 0 20px; list-style: disc; line-height: 1.8; color: #1e3a8a; font-size: 0.9375rem;">
                                    <li>Accept <strong>Terms and Conditions</strong>
                                    </li>
                                    <li>Security Policy that  only one user is allowed per device which states "<i>I agree that enrolling a new customer will remove the existing account linked on this device.</i>"
                                    </li>
                            </div>
                    </section>
                    <div class="cgs-callout success">
                        <div class="cgs-callout-icon">
                            <i class="fa fa-check-circle"></i>
                        </div>
                        <div class="cgs-callout-content">
                            <strong>Account Created!</strong>
                            <p>Once you see the confirmation screen, your account is ready. You can now proceed to set up your profile and configure your wallet.</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <!-- First Login & Setup -->
                    <section class="cgs-section" id="sec-first-login">
                        <h2 class="cgs-section-title">First Login & Setup</h2>
                        <p>After creating your account, you'll be guided through the initial setup wizard. Here's what to expect:</p>
                        <h3 class="cgs-section-subtitle" id="sec-profile-setup">Profile Setup</h3>
                        <div class="cgs-steps">
                            <div class="cgs-step" data-step="1">
                                <h4 class="cgs-step-title">Add your personal details</h4>
                                <div class="cgs-step-content">
                                    Enter your full name as it appears on your government-issued ID. Optionally, add a profile photo for easy identification during P2P transfers.
</div>
                            </div>
                            <div class="cgs-step" data-step="2">
                                <h4 class="cgs-step-title">Set up security</h4>
                                <div class="cgs-step-content">
                                    Configure your preferred authentication method:
                                    <ul>
                                        <li>
                                            <strong>PIN Code</strong> — Set a 6-digit PIN for quick access
                                        </li>
                                        <li>
                                            <strong>Biometric</strong> — Enable Face ID or fingerprint authentication
                                        </li>
                                        <li>We recommend enabling both for maximum security</li>
                                    </ul>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                            <div class="cgs-step" data-step="3">
                                <h4 class="cgs-step-title">Enable notifications</h4>
                                <div class="cgs-step-content">
                                    Allow push notifications to receive instant payment confirmations, security alerts, and promotional offers. You can customize notification preferences later in <a onclick="load_page('consumer_settings')" style="color: var(--color-primary, #2563eb); cursor: pointer;">Settings</a>.

                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <h3 class="cgs-section-subtitle" id="sec-wallet-setup">Wallet Configuration</h3>
                        <div class="cgs-steps">
                            <div class="cgs-step" data-step="1">
                                <h4 class="cgs-step-title">Personalized your profile</h4>
                                <div class="cgs-step-content">Set a profile picture for your wallet account</div>
                            </div>
                            <div class="cgs-step" data-step="2">
                                <h4 class="cgs-step-title">Managing Notification Preferences</h4>
                                <div class="cgs-step-content">You can turn on/off a notification option, based on your own preferences.</div>
                            </div>
                            <div class="cgs-step" data-step="3">
                                <h4 class="cgs-step-title">Complete the setup</h4>
                                <div class="cgs-step-content">
                                    Tap <strong>Finish Setup</strong> to land on your wallet dashboard. You're ready to start making payments!
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="cgs-callout info">
                            <div class="cgs-callout-icon">
                                <i class="fa fa-lightbulb"></i>
                            </div>
                            <div class="cgs-callout-content">
                                <strong>Tip: Complete Verification Early</strong>
                                <p>Verification process may take 24 to 48 hours, it is advisable to complete the profile asap in order to gain full access to mPay Wallet features.</p>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </section>
                    <!-- Screenshots -->
                    <section class="cgs-screenshots" id="sec-screenshots">
                        <h2 class="cgs-section-title">Setup Walkthrough</h2>
                        <p>Here's a visual overview of the key screens you'll encounter during setup:</p>
                        <div class="cgs-screenshot-grid">
                            <div class="cgs-screenshot-item">
                                <div class="cgs-screenshot-mockup">
                                    <div class="mockup-header"></div>
                                    <div class="mockup-icon">
                                        <i class="fa fa-hand-peace"></i>
                                    </div>
                                    <div class="mockup-label">Welcome Screen</div>
                                    <div class="mockup-sublabel">Create Account or Sign In</div>
                                </div>
                                <p class="cgs-screenshot-caption">Step 1: Welcome Screen</p>
                            </div>
                            <div class="cgs-screenshot-item">
                                <div class="cgs-screenshot-mockup">
                                    <div class="mockup-header"></div>
                                    <div class="mockup-icon">
                                        <i class="fa fa-mobile-alt"></i>
                                    </div>
                                    <div class="mockup-label">Phone Verification</div>
                                    <div class="mockup-sublabel">Enter OTP Code</div>
                                </div>
                                <p class="cgs-screenshot-caption">Step 2: Verify Phone</p>
                            </div>
                            <div class="cgs-screenshot-item">
                                <div class="cgs-screenshot-mockup">
                                    <div class="mockup-header"></div>
                                    <div class="mockup-icon">
                                        <i class="fa fa-fingerprint"></i>
                                    </div>
                                    <div class="mockup-label">Security Setup</div>
                                    <div class="mockup-sublabel">PIN & Biometric</div>
                                </div>
                                <p class="cgs-screenshot-caption">Step 3: Set Up Security</p>
                            </div>
                            <div class="cgs-screenshot-item">
                                <div class="cgs-screenshot-mockup">
                                    <div class="mockup-header"></div>
                                    <div class="mockup-icon">
                                        <i class="fa fa-user-circle"></i>
                                    </div>
                                    <div class="mockup-label">Profile Info</div>
                                    <div class="mockup-sublabel">Name & Photo</div>
                                </div>
                                <p class="cgs-screenshot-caption">Step 4: Your Profile</p>
                            </div>
                            <div class="cgs-screenshot-item">
                                <div class="cgs-screenshot-mockup">
                                    <div class="mockup-header"></div>
                                    <div class="mockup-icon">
                                        <i class="fa fa-wallet"></i>
                                    </div>
                                    <div class="mockup-label">Wallet Setup</div>
                                    <div class="mockup-sublabel">Currency & Funding</div>
                                </div>
                                <p class="cgs-screenshot-caption">Step 5: Configure Wallet</p>
                            </div>
                            <div class="cgs-screenshot-item">
                                <div class="cgs-screenshot-mockup">
                                    <div class="mockup-header"></div>
                                    <div class="mockup-icon">
                                        <i class="fa fa-check-circle"></i>
                                    </div>
                                    <div class="mockup-label">All Set!</div>
                                    <div class="mockup-sublabel">Dashboard Ready</div>
                                </div>
                                <p class="cgs-screenshot-caption">Step 6: Ready to Go!</p>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </section>
                    <!-- FAQ Accordion -->
                    <section class="cgs-faq" id="sec-faq">
                        <h2 class="cgs-faq-title">Frequently Asked Questions</h2>
                        <div class="cgs-accordion">
                            <div class="cgs-accordion-item">
                                <button class="cgs-accordion-trigger" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="faq-panel-1">
                                    <span>Can I use mPay Wallet on multiple devices?</span>
                                    <i class="fa fa-chevron-down"></i>
                                </button>
                                <div class="cgs-accordion-panel" id="faq-panel-1" role="region">
                                    <div class="cgs-accordion-panel-inner">Yes, you can sign in to your mPay account on multiple devices. However, for security reasons, <b>only one device can be active at a time</b>. Signing in on a new device will automatically sign you out of the previous one.&nbsp;
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                            <div class="cgs-accordion-item">
                                <button class="cgs-accordion-trigger" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="faq-panel-2">
                                    <span>What if I don't receive the OTP code?</span>
                                    <i class="fa fa-chevron-down"></i>
                                </button>
                                <div class="cgs-accordion-panel" id="faq-panel-2" role="region">
                                    <div class="cgs-accordion-panel-inner">
                                        If you don't receive the OTP within 60 seconds, tap the "Resend Code" button. Make sure your phone has signal reception and SMS is not blocked. If the issue persists, try the "Call Me" option for voice verification. Check our <a onclick="load_page('consumer_troubleshooting')">Troubleshooting guide</a> for more solutions.
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                            <div class="cgs-accordion-item">
                                <button class="cgs-accordion-trigger" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="faq-panel-3">
                                    <span>Is there a minimum deposit to start using the wallet?</span>
                                    <i class="fa fa-chevron-down"></i>
                                </button>
                                <div class="cgs-accordion-panel" id="faq-panel-3" role="region">
                                    <div class="cgs-accordion-panel-inner">
                                        No, there is no minimum deposit required. You can create your account and explore the app without adding any funds. When you're ready to make a payment, you can fund your wallet with any amount. Check <a onclick="load_page('consumer_wallet_management')">Wallet Management</a> for funding options and limits.
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                            <div class="cgs-accordion-item">
                                <button class="cgs-accordion-trigger" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="faq-panel-4">
                                    <span>Can I change my phone number after registration?</span>
                                    <i class="fa fa-chevron-down"></i>
                                </button>
                                <div class="cgs-accordion-panel" id="faq-panel-4" role="region">
                                    <div class="cgs-accordion-panel-inner">
                                        Yes, you can update your phone number from the Settings page. You'll need to verify your identity and the new phone number via OTP. The old number will be unlinked after successful verification. For security, there's a 24-hour cooling period before certain features are re-enabled after a number change.
</div>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                            <div class="cgs-accordion-item">
                                <button class="cgs-accordion-trigger" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="faq-panel-5">
                                    <span>What should I do if the app crashes during setup?</span>
                                    <i class="fa fa-chevron-down"></i>
                                </button>
                                <div class="cgs-accordion-panel" id="faq-panel-5" role="region">
                                    <div class="cgs-accordion-panel-inner">
                                        If the app crashes during setup, simply reopen it. Your progress is saved automatically at each step. If the problem persists, try clearing the app cache (Android) or reinstalling the app (iOS). Make sure you have the latest version installed. Visit our <a onclick="load_page('consumer_troubleshooting')">Troubleshooting</a> page for more help.
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                            <div class="cgs-accordion-item">
                                <button class="cgs-accordion-trigger" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="faq-panel-6">
                                    <span>Is my personal data secure during registration?</span>
                                    <i class="fa fa-chevron-down"></i>
                                </button>
                                <div class="cgs-accordion-panel" id="faq-panel-6" role="region">
                                    <div class="cgs-accordion-panel-inner">
                                        Absolutely. All data transmitted during registration is encrypted using industry-standard TLS 1.3. Your personal information is stored securely and never shared with third parties without your consent. Read our <a onclick="load_page('privacy_policy')">Privacy Policy</a> for complete details on how we handle your data.
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </section>
                    <!-- Prev/Next pagination -->
                    <div class="cgs-pagination" id="cgs_prev_next">
                        <a class="cgs-pagination-btn prev" onclick="load_page('consumer_docs_home')"> <span class="pag-label"><i class="fa fa-arrow-left"></i> Previous</span> <span class="pag-title">Consumer Docs Home</span> </a>
                        <a class="cgs-pagination-btn next" onclick="load_page('consumer_account_setup')"> <span class="pag-label">Next <i class="fa fa-arrow-right"></i></span> <span class="pag-title">Account Setup & Verification</span> </a>
                    </div>
                </main>
